# layout-generator
A script to start multiple terminals on diferent hosts according to a hosts file using the terminator layout option.






IDEAS:
Reject repeated hosts 
Set de PS1 of each park with the name from the hostsfile
Set groups according to windows
Set groups according to host tipology
Group terminals by park tipology (~ kinda done)






HISTORY:

2017/12/13    Set number of windows, terminals, and terminal-spots using number of screens and hosts.
2017/12/15    Distribute hosts accross windows

